{"tid":28884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新蕭析：林鄭出選即CY不能出閘……","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T08:25:58.000Z","uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a310145388a20643f020b9f07b76e723d34f7355","tid":28884,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"最新蕭析：中聯辦轉軚支持葉劉 梁振英仲有無機入閘？<br />\n<br />\n拒答議員提問風波，梁振英沒出席會議是真的，但他是否不知情就可以商榷，不過這兩天關於特首選舉的新發展，就值得認真重新思考。<br />\n<br />\n首先，所有派別的人都沒有否認過今屆特首選舉，中央是持開放態度予所有認為是政治上可靠的人去競選。這一點我是接受的。而大概從半年前開始，我質疑梁振英是否能順利出閘，而質疑是因林鄭而起的，那時林鄭突然回躍，似乎有想參選的意向，於是我立即覺察，如林鄭出選即CY不能出閘&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"af03717ab8ad7b7dca1116beb8cf76b2409125af","tid":28884,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"燒藥丸頭號梁粉黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae542b051dc2d5dd687afad127e42cd6ca117b87","tid":28884,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"支持燒山<br />\n多謝燒山<br />\n19:嘿嘿"},{"pid":"94ca0e2efd6a78088231fdc4ab5b90da7c41fc43","tid":28884,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"林鄭molamola"},{"pid":"293a1be40cdf3e30edbc017cb1fcc745870ae8e1","tid":28884,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭molamola</blockquote><br />\n所以689 sure win"},{"pid":"9f947224d1e4f3cce47c2125abe939013d04ebf8","tid":28884,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"燒山好嘢～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66e8828d51ed1982e56f9816aabd722ba361705","tid":28884,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"屌你又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3295b24a35d07efe180003d19987ae60b887af3f","tid":28884,"uid":59